snippet.title: U.S.G. - A New Beginning: Stage 4 Hard Mode
snippet.description:
Me playing "U.S.G. - A New Beginning" on hard mode with all the stuff on level 5. 
Woah, pretty laggy this time. I'm sorry for that *kicks Hypercam*
Anyway, I hate this stage, because of the enemys which explode and this really annoying boss.

This is stage 4.


I couldn't record the sound, so I had to put in some music in the video. I've used the same music for the game which you can hear in the video, however, the music itself doesn't appear in the game. It's music/remix from Touhou Project.
